al, goes on an adventure with her brother to save the spirit world and other magical beings like her.',2014,93,3,NULL,'SongoftheSea.jpg',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(59,'The Tale of The Princess Kaguya',NULL,'Found inside a shining stalk of bamboo by an old bamboo cutter and his wife, a tiny girl grows rapidly into an exquisite young lady. The mysterious young princess enthralls all who encounter her - but ultimately she must confront her fate, the punishment for her crime.',2013,137,3,NULL,'TheTaleofThePrincessKaguya.jpg',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(60,'12 Years a Slave','노예 12년','In the antebellum United States, Solomon Northup, a free black man from upstate New York, is abducted and sold into slavery.',2013,134,1,NULL,'12YearsaSlave.jpg','2014-02-27',187733202,56671993,20000000),(61,'The Wolf of Wall Street','울프 오브 월 스트리트','Based on the true story of Jordan Belfort, from his rise to a wealthy stock-broker living the high life to his fall involving crime, corruption and the federal government.',2013,180,1,NULL,'TheWolfofWallStreet.jpg','2014-01-09',392000694,116900694,100000000),(62,'American Hustle','아메리칸 허슬','A con man, Irving Rosenfeld, along with his seductive partner Sydney Prosser, is forced to work for a wild FBI agent, Richie DiMaso, who pushes them into a world of Jersey powerbrokers and mafia.',2013,138,1,NULL,'AmericanHustle.jpg','2014-02-20',251171807,150117807,40000000),(63,'Nebraska','네브라스카','An aging, booze-addled father makes the trip from Montana to Nebraska with his estranged son in order to claim a million-dollar Mega Sweepstakes Marketing prize.',2013,115,1,NULL,'Nebraska.jpg','2013-03-20',17654912,17654912,12000000),(64,'Captain Phillips','캡틴 필립스','The true story of Captain Richard Phillips and the 2009 hijacking by Somali pirates of the US-flagged MV Maersk Alabama, the first American cargo ship to be hijacked in two hundred years.',2013,134,2,NULL,'CaptainPhillips.jpg','2013-10-23',218791811,107100855,55000000),(65,'Philomena','필로미나의 기적','A world-weary p