 Nolan invited Franklin to be overall VFX supervisor for his film Inception. Franklin‘s work on the film earned him an Oscar as well as BAFTA and VES wins. Franklin continued his working relationship with Nolan as VFX supervisor for The Dark Knight Rises.','','Cheshire, England, UK','1900-01-01',NULL,NULL,''),(87,'Andrew Lockley','앤드류 로클레이','Andrew Lockley was born on May 5, 1971 in London, England. He is known for his work on The Dark Knight (2008), Inception (2010) and The Dark Knight Rises (2012).','','London, England, UK','1971-05-05',NULL,NULL,''),(88,'Ian Hunter','이안 헌터','Director/VFX Supervisor and co-founder of New Deal Studios, Ian is multi-disciplined artist who has established himself as a visionary storyteller in the field of motion picture visual effects and production for over 25 years. Bringing his unique style and creative vision to each of his projects, Hunter has won 3 VES Awards for his work including sequences in The Dark Knight (2008) and Inception (2010) . He was recently a visual effect supervisor on the film Interstellar (2014) Hunter‘s directorial debut was the award winning Short Allure (2009) and two national Subway Commercials. Ever the creator, Ian is parlaying his experience in visual effects and film design into the cutting edge virtual reality world with his first project Kaiju Fury! (2014)','','','1900-01-01',NULL,NULL,'IanHunter.jpg'),(89,'Scott R. Fisher','스콧 R. 피셔','Scott R. Fisher is known for his work on Inception (2010), The Dark Knight Rises (2012) and Titanic (1997).','','','1900-01-01',NULL,NULL,''),(90,'Dan Deleeuw',NULL,'Dan Deleeuw is known for his work on Iron Man 3 (2013), Captain America: The Winter Soldier (2014) and Armageddon (1998).','','','1900-01-01',NULL,NULL,''),(91,'Russell Earl','러셀 얼','Russell Earl is known for his work on Pirates of the Caribbean: The Curse of the Black Pearl (2003), Harry Potter and the Sorcerer‘s Stone (2001) and Star Trek (2009).','','','1900-01-01',NULL,NULL,''),(92,'Bryan Grill','브라이언 