ve editorial house known for its commercial work for such clients as BMW, HP, and Nike.\"\r\n\r\nAngus is a film editor who has won the Academy Awards for Film Editing twice in a row, both for David Fincher movies (The Social Network and The Girl With the Dragon Tattoo). His very first Academy nomination was for The Curious Case of Benjamin Button, also a David Fincher movie. Angus often works together with Kirk Baxter.','','','1900-01-01',NULL,NULL,'AngusWall.jpg'),(534,'Kirk Baxter',NULL,'Kirk Baxter was born in 1972 in Sydney, New South Wales, Australia. He is known for his work on Gone Girl (2014), The Social Network (2010) and The Curious Case of Benjamin Button (2008).','','Sydney, New South Wales, Australia','1900-01-01',NULL,NULL,'KirkBaxter.jpg'),(535,'Anne-Sophie Bion',NULL,'-','','','1900-01-01',NULL,NULL,'Anne-SophieBion.jpg'),(536,'Kevin Tent',NULL,'Kevin Tent is an editor, known for The Descendants (2011), Sideways (2004) and Blow (2001).','','','1900-01-01',NULL,NULL,''),(537,'Thelma Schoonmaker','델마 스쿤메이커','Thelma Schoonmaker was born on January 3, 1940 in Algeria as Thelma Colbert Schoonmaker. She is an editor, known for The Departed (2006), Goodfellas (1990) and The Wolf of Wall Street (2013). She was previously married to Michael Powell.','Thelma Colbert Schoonmaker','Algeria','1940-01-03',NULL,NULL,''),(538,'Christopher Tellefsen',NULL,'Christopher Tellefsen was born in September 1957. In 1979 he attended New York‘s Cooper Union for the Advancement of Science and Art but as a student of photography and fine arts,becoming interested in experimental film-making after taking classes with Bob Breere. Shortly after graduation he was given a job assisting Ralph Rosenbloom cutting an independent movie and later became apprentice to another renowned editor Thelma Schoonmaker before,in 1990,taking his first job as a cutter in his own right for Whit Stillman‘s ‘Metropolitan.‘ Since then he has not only achieved success in the field of editing (including an