',NULL,NULL,'CharlesFerguson.jpg'),(938,'Audrey Marrs','오드리 마스','Audrey Marrs is a producer, known for Inside Job (2010), No End in Sight (2007) and The 83rd Annual Academy Awards (2011).','','USA','1970-06-25',NULL,NULL,'AudreyMarrs.jpg'),(939,'Richard Robbins',NULL,'Richard Robbins was born on December 5, 1969. He is a writer and producer, known for Peter Jennings Reporting: LAPD (2004), Peter Jennings Reporting: I Have a Dream (2003) and Operation Homecoming: Writing the Wartime Experience (2007). He has been married to Katherine Collins Pope since June 2001','','','1969-11-05',NULL,NULL,''),(940,'Michael Moore',NULL,'Michael Francis Moore was born in Flint, Michigan on April 23, 1954, and was raised in Davison, Michigan. He is the son of Helen Veronica (Wall), a secretary, and Francis Richard Moore, who worked on an auto assembly line. He has Irish, as well as English and Scottish, ancestry.\r\n\r\nMoore studied journalism at the University of Michigan-Flint, and also pursued other hobbies such as gun shooting, for which he even won a competition. Michael began his journalistic career writing for the school newspaper \"The Michigan Times,\" and after dropping out of college briefly worked as editor for \"Mother Jones.\"\r\n\r\nHe then turned to filmmaking, and to earn the money for the budget of his first film Roger & Me (1989) he ran neighborhood bingo games. The success of this film launched his career as one of America‘s best-known and most controversial documentarians. He has produced a string of documentary films and TV series predominantly about the same subject: attacks on corrupt politicians and greedy business corporations. He landed his first big hit with Bowling for Columbine (2002) about the bad points of the right to bear arms in America, which earned him an Oscar and a big reputation. He then shook the world with his even bigger hit Fahrenheit 9/11 (2004), making fun of President George W. Bush. This is the highest-grossing documentary of all time. Michael is known for having the guts to give his opinion in public, which not many people are courageous enough to do, and for that is respected by many.','Michael Francis Moore','Flint, Michigan, USA','1954-04-23',NULL,NULL,'MichaelMoore.jpg'),(941,'Meghan O‘Hara',NULL,'Meghan O‘Hara is a producer and director, known for Bowling for Columbine (2002), Fahrenheit 9/11 (2004) and Sicko (2007).','','','1900-01-01',NULL,NULL,''),(942,'Andrea Nix','안드레아 닉스','Andrea Nix is a producer and production manager, known for War Dance (2007), Life According to Sam (2013) and Inocente (2012). She is married to Sean Fine.','','','1900-01-01',NULL,NULL,'AndreaNix.jpg'),(943,'Sean Fine','션 파인','Sean Fine is a producer and cinematographer, known for War Dance (2007), Life According to Sam (2013) and Inocente (2012).','','','1900-01-01',NULL,NULL,''),(944,'Marjane Satrapi',NULL,'Marjane Satrapi was born on November 22, 1969 in Rasht, Iran. She is a director and writer, known for Persepolis (2007), Chicken with Plums (2011) and The Voices (2014). She is married to Mattias Ripa. She was previously married to Reza.','','Rasht, Iran','1900-01-01',NULL,NULL,'MarjaneSatrapi.jpg'),(945,'Vincent Paronnaud',NULL,'Vincent Paronnaud was born in 1970 in La Rochelle, Charente-Maritime, France. He is a writer and director, known for Persepolis (2007), Chicken with Plums (2011) and Raging Blues (2004).','','La Rochelle, Charente-Maritime, France','1900-01-01',NULL,NULL,''),(946,'Ash Brannon',NULL,'Ash Brannon is known for his work on Toy Story 2 (1999), Toy Story (1995) and Surf‘s Up (2007).','','','1900-01-01',NULL,NULL,''),(947,'Chris Buck',NULL,'Chris Buck is known for his work on Frozen (2013), Pocahontas (1995) and Surf‘s Up (2007).','','','1900-01-01',NULL,NULL,'ChrisBuck.jpg'),(948,'Laurent Witz',NULL,'Laurent Witz is a director and writer, known for Mr Hublot (2013), The Oscars (2014) and Festival Road Trip (2008).','','','1900-01-01',NULL,NULL,''),(949,'Alexandre Espigares',NULL,'Alexandre 