','허버트 데이비스','','','','1900-01-01',NULL,NULL,''),(2514,'Oren Jacoby','오렌 자코비','Oren Jacoby is a producer and director, known for Constantine‘s Sword (2007), The Return Ticket (1988) and Sister Rose‘s Passion (2004).','','','1900-01-01',NULL,NULL,'OrenJacoby.jpg'),(2515,'Steve Kalafer','스티브 칼리퍼','','','','1900-01-01',NULL,NULL,''),(2516,'Ross Kauffman','로스 카우프만','Ross Kauffman is a producer and cinematographer, known for Born Into Brothels: Calcutta‘s Red Light Kids (2004), E-Team (2014) and Comic-Con Episode IV: A Fan‘s Hope (2011).','','','1900-01-01',NULL,NULL,'RossKauffman.jpg'),(2517,'Zana Briski','자나 브리스키','Zana Briski was born in London, England. She is a director and writer, known for Born Into Brothels: Calcutta‘s Red Light Kids (2004), The WIN Awards 2006 (2006) and The 77th Annual Academy Awards (2005).','','London, England, UK','1900-01-01',NULL,NULL,'ZanaBriski.jpg'),(2518,'Luigi Falorni','','Luigi Falorni was born on January 4, 1971 in Florence, Tuscany, Italy. He is a cinematographer and director, known for The Story of the Weeping Camel (2003), Heart of Fire (2008) and Fools and Heroes (1997).','','Florence, Tuscany, Italy','1971-01-04',NULL,NULL,''),(2519,'Byambasuren Davaa','','Byambasuren Davaa was born in 1971 in Ulan Bator, Mongolia. She is a director and writer, known for The Story of the Weeping Camel (2003), The Cave of the Yellow Dog (2005) and The Two Horses of Genghis Khan (2009).','','Ulan Bator, Mongolia','1900-01-01',NULL,NULL,''),(2520,'Morgan Spurlock','모건 스펄록','Morgan Spurlock was born on November 7, 1970 in Parkersburg, West Virginia, USA as Morgan Valentine Spurlock. He is a producer and writer, known for Super Size Me (2004), The Greatest Movie Ever Sold (2011) and Where in the World Is Osama Bin Laden? (2008).','Morgan Valentine Spurlock','Parkersburg, West Virginia, USA','1970-11-07',NULL,NULL,'MorganSpurlock.jpg'),(2521,'Lauren Lazin','','Lauren Lazin is a producer and director, known for Tupac: Resurrection (2003), TeenNick Halo Awards (2009) and I‘m Still Here: Real Diaries of Young People Who Lived During the Holocaust (2005). She is married to Norm Green.','','','1900-01-01',NULL,NULL,''),(2522,'Karolyn Ali','캐롤린 알리','Karolyn Ali is a producer, known for Tupac: Resurrection (2003), Klash (1995) and Unsung (2008).','','','1900-01-01',NULL,NULL,''),(2523,'Eddie Schmidt','에디 슈미트','Eddie Schmidt was born on August 29, 1970 in the USA as Edward Robert Schmidt. He is a producer, known for This Film Is Not Yet Rated (2006), Valentine Road (2013) and Twist of Faith (2004). He has been married to Rachel Kamerman since June 24, 2001.','Edward Robert Schmidt','USA','1970-08-29',NULL,NULL,'EddieSchmidt.jpg'),(2524,'Alejandro Amenabar','알레한드로 아메나바르','Is the son of a Spanish mother and a Chilean father. His family moved back to Spain when he was 1 year old, and he grew up and studied in Madrid. He wrote, produced and directed his first short film La cabeza at the age of 19, and he was 23 when he directed his feature debut Thesis (1996). His film Open Your Eyes (1997) was a huge success in Spain and was distributed worldwide. It was remade in Hollywood by Cameron Crowe as Vanilla Sky (2001), starring Tom Cruise, Penelope Cruz (also the star of the original version) and Cameron Diaz. The Others (2001) is Amenabar‘s first English language film.','Alejandro Fernando Amenabar Canto','Santiago de Chile, Chile','1972-03-31',NULL,NULL,'AlejandroAmenabar.jpg'),(2525,'Kay Pollak','케이 폴락','','Kay Gunnar Leopold Pollak','Gamlestaden, Gothenburg, Vastra Gotalands lan, Sweden','1938-03-21',NULL,NULL,''),(2526,'Oliver Hirschbiegel','올리버 히르쉬비겔','Born in Hamburg, Germany, in 1957. In his teens he left high school and worked as a cooker in a boat.\r\n\r\nThen he studied painting and graphism in the Academy of arts in Hamburg where he also started experimenting with video and photography. Those experimental movies attracted the attention of some producers of the German TV.\r\n\r\nHirschbiegel became popular thanks to his tv movies (especially dramas and thrillers). In 2001 he shot his first movie for cinema: \"Das Experiment\" that won several awards in many festivals all around the world. That movie is an intense investigation of the aggressive behaviour in a simulated prison environment.\r\n\r\nHis second movie, \"Mein letzter Film\", released in 2002, is a 90 minutes‘ monologue about a woman in her fifties who wants to re-start his life.\r\n\r\nIn 2004 \"Downfall\" was released, his third movie, and till now his greatest success. \"Downfall\" is about the last 12 days of life of Adolf Hitler narrated out of the sight of her young secretary, Traudl Junge. That movie has stirred up much controversy because it portrays Hitler and the Nazis as human beings and not just as evil.\r\n\r\nHirschbiegel has demonstrated in all his movies to be an specialist of dramas set in claustrophobic environments.','','Hamburg, Germany','1957-11-29',NULL,NULL,'OliverHirschbiegel.jpg'),(2527,'Darrell Roodt','대럴 루트','','','Johannesburg, South Africa','1962-04-28',NULL,NULL,'DarrellRoodt.jpg'),(2528,'Bill Damaschke','빌 다마스케','Bill Damaschke was born on November 20, 1963 in Chicago, Illinois, USA.','','Chicago, Illinois, USA','1963-11-20',NULL,NULL,''),(2529,'Andrew Adamson','앤드류 아담슨','Andrew Adamson was born on December 1, 1966 in Auckland, New Zealand. He is a producer and director, known for Shrek 2 (2004), The Chronicles of Narnia: The Lion, the Witch and the Wardrobe (2005) and The Chronicles of Narnia: Prince Caspian (2008).','','Auckland, New Zealand','1966-12-01',NULL,NULL,'AndrewAdamson.jpg'),(2530,'Barrie M. Osborne','배리 오스본','배리 오스본은 미국 뉴욕에서 태어난 프로듀서이자 프로덕션 매니저이다. 그는 \"반지의 제왕\" 시리즈와 \"매트릭스\" 시리즈의 프로듀서로 유명하며, \"반지의 제왕: 왕의 귀환(2003년)\"으로 아카데미 작품상을 수상했다.','','New York City, New York, USA','1944-02-07',NULL,NULL,'BarrieMOsborne.jpg'),(2531,'Fran Walsh','프란 월쉬','프란 월쉬는 뉴질랜드에서 태어난 작가로, 반지의 제왕 시리즈의 각본을 썼다. 그녀는 1987년에 피터 잭슨과 결혼했으며 두 자녀를 두고 있다. 그녀는 \"반지의 제왕: 왕의 귀환(2003년)\"으로 아카데미 작품상, 각색상, 음악상을 수상했다.','','Wellington, New Zealand','1959-01-10',NULL,NULL,'FranWalsh.jpg'),(2532,'Ross Katz','로스 커츠','Nominated for Academy Awards for co-producing Todd Field‘s In the Bedroom (2001), and Sofia Coppola‘s Lost in Translation (2003). Katz has had three films in competition at the Sundance Film Festival.','','Philadelphia, Pennsylvania, USA','1971-05-19',NULL,NULL,'RossKatz.jpg'),(2533,'Sofia Coppola','소피아 코폴라','소피아 코폴라는 미국 뉴욕에서 태어난 감독이자 배우로 감독 프랜시스 포드 코폴라의 딸이며, \"ShowWhere(2010년)\", \"사랑도 통역이 되나요(2003년)\", \"마리 앙트와네트(2006년)\"의 감독으로 알려져 있다. 그녀는 스파이크 존스와 결혼했으며, \"사랑도 통역이 되나요(2003년)\"으로 아카데미 각본상을 수상했다.','Sofia Carmina Coppola','New York City, New York, USA','1971-05-14',NULL,NULL,'SofiaCoppola.jpg'),(2534,'Elijah Wood','일라이저 우드','일라이저 우드는 미국인 배우로, 피터 잭슨의 반지의 제왕 3부작으로 세계적으로 유명해졌다. 그는 아역 배우 출신으로, 로버트 로드리게즈의 \"패컬티\"에 출연했으며, 그후 \"씬 시티\"와 \"이터널 선샤인\"에도 출연했다.','Elijah Jordan Wood','Cedar Rapids, Iowa, USA','1981-01-28',NULL,NULL,'ElijahWood.jpg'),(2535,'Sean Astin','션 애스틴','션 오스틴은 미국 출신의 배우로, 스티븐 스필버그가 제작하고 리처드 도너가 감독한 \"구니스\"에서 미키역으로 출연한 것이 그의 첫 영화였다. 그 후 \"루디(1993년)\"등의 영화에 출연했다. 그를 세계에 알린 영화는 피터 잭슨 감독의 반지의 제왕 3부작으로, 그는 반지 운반자 프로도와 함께 긴 여정을 떠나는 샘 와이즈 갬지역을 맡았다. 그는 영화 제작에도 재능이 있어, \"Kangaroo Court(1994년)\"으로 아카데미 단편 영화상 후보에 올랐다.','Sean Patrick Duke','Santa Monica, California, USA','1971-02-25',NULL,NULL,'SeanAstin.jpg'),(2536,'Orlando Bloom','올란도 블룸','올란도 블룸은 영국 출신의 배우로, \"블랙 호크 다운\"등의 영화에 출연했다. 그를 세계에 알린 영화는 피터 잭슨의 반지의 제왕 3부작으로, 그는 요정 레골라스 역을 맡아 세계적인 스타가 되었다. 그후 캐러비안의 해적 시리즈에 출연해 반지의 제왕에 못지 않은 성공을 거두었으며, 리들리 스콧의 \"킹덤 오브 해븐\"등의 영화에 출연했다.','Orlando Jonathan Blanchard Bloom','Canterbury, Kent, England, UK','1977-01-13',NULL,NULL,'OrlandoBloom.jpg'),(2537,'Samuel Goldwyn Jr.','사무엘 골드윈 주니어','Samuel Goldwyn Jr. was born on September 7, 1926 in Los Angeles, California, USA as Samuel John Goldwyn Jr. He is known for his work on Master and Commander: The Far Side of the World (2003), The Secret Life of Walter Mitty (2013) and Mystic Pizza (1988). He was married to Patricia Strawn, Peggy Elliott and Jennifer Howard. He died on January 9','Samuel John Goldwyn Jr.','Los Angeles, California, USA','1926-09-07',NULL,NULL,'SamuelGoldwynJr.jpg'),(2538,'Peter Weir','피터 위어','피터 위어는 호주 출신의 감독으로, \"트루먼 쇼(1998년)\", \"마스터 앤드 커맨더(2003년)\", \"죽은 시인의 사회(1989년)\"등의 영화로 유명하다. 그는 아카데미 감독상 후보에 4회, 작품상 1회, 각본상에 1회 후보로 총 6회 아카데미 후보에 올랐으나, 2015년 현재 한번도 수상하지는 못했다.','Peter Lindsay Weir','Sydney, New South Wales, Australia','1944-08-21',NULL,NULL,'PeterWeir.jpg'),(2539,'Duncan Henderson','던칸 헨더슨','Duncan Henderson is a producer and assistant director, known for Harry Potter and the Sorcerer‘s Stone (2001), Dead Poets Society (1989) and Outbreak (1995). He is married to Michele P. Henderson. They have one child.','','','1900-01-01',NULL,NULL,''),(2540,'Judie Hoyt','주디 홀트','','','','1900-01-01',NULL,NULL,''),(2541,'Gary Ross','게리 로스','게리 로스는 미국 출신의 감독이자 작가로, 톰 행크스의 \"빅(1983년)\"을 연출한 것으로 유명하다. 그는 아카데미 작품상 후보(시비스킷), 각본상 후보(시비스킷, 데이브, 빅) 등 총 4회 아카데미상 후보에 올랐다.','','Los Angeles, California, USA','1956-11-03',NULL,NULL,'GaryRoss.jpg'),(2543,'John Rhys-Davies','존 라이스-데이비스','영국 출신의 존 라이스-데이비스는 스티블 스필버그와 조지 루카스의 블록 버스터 \"레이더스: 잃어버린 성궤의 추적자들(1981년)\"과 \"인디아나 존스와 최후의 성전(1989년)\"에 출연하여 세계에 알려졌다. 그 후 그는 피터 잭슨의 반지의 제왕 3부작에 난쟁이 김리 역으로 출연했으며, 그 외에 \"07 리빙 데이라이트(1987년)\"등에도 출연했다.','','Ammanford, Wales, UK','1944-05-05',NULL,NULL,'JohnRhysDavies.jpg'),(2544,'Billy Boyd','빌리 보이드','영국 출신의 배우 빌리 보이드는 어릴적 스타워즈를 보고 배우가 되기로 결심했으며, 피터 잭슨의 반지의 제왕 3부작에 피핀역으로 출연하여 세계적으로 알려졌다.','William Boyd','Glasgow, Scotland, UK','1968-08-28',NULL,NULL,'BillyBoyd.jpg'),(2545,'Dominic Monaghan','도미닉 모나한','도미닉 모나한은 독일 출신의 배우로, 피터 잭슨의 반지의 제왕 3부작에서 호빗 메리 역을 맡아 세계적으로 유명해졌다.','Dominic Bernard Patrick Luke Monaghan','Berlin, Germany','1976-12-08',NULL,NULL,'DominicMonaghan.jpg'),(2546,'Sean Bean','숀 빈','영국 출신의 배우 숀빈은 20년간 영화, 라디오, 텔레비젼과 연극 무대에 서온 베테랑 배우이다. 그는 수 없이 많은 영화와 TV에 출연했으며, 수 없이 많은 히트 영화로 세계에 알려졌다. 그는 피터 잭슨의 반지의 제왕 3부작에서 보로미르 역을 맡았으며, 볼프강 피터슨의 \"트로이\"에서 오딧세우스 역을 맡았고, 그외 수 없이 많은 영화에서 주요 배역으로 출연했다. 최근에는 TV 시리즈 \"왕좌의 게임\"에서 에다드 스타크 역을 연기한 것으로 유명하다.','Shaun Mark Bean','Sheffield, South Yorkshire, England, UK','1959-04-17',NULL,NULL,'SeanBean.jpg'),(2547,'Bernard Hill','버나드 힐','버나드 힐은 영국 출신의 배우로, 피터 잭슨의 반지의 제왕 3부작에서 세오덴 왕 역을 맡은 것으로 유명하다. 그는 또한 제임스 카메론의 \"타이티닉(1997년)\"에서 타이타닉호의 스미스 선장역을 연기한 것으로 세계적으로 알려졌다.','','Manchester, England, UK','1944-12-17',NULL,NULL,'BernardHill.jpg'),(2548,'Karl Urban','칼 어반','칼 아번은 뉴질랜드 출신의 배우로, 주로 액션 영화에 출연했다. 그는 피터 잭슨의 반지의 제왕 3부작에 에오메르 역으로 출연해 세계적으로 알려졌으며, \"본 슈프리머시\", \"리딕\"등에 출연한 것으로도 유명하다. 최근에는 스타 트랙 리부트 시리즈에서 엔터프라이즈호의 군의관 본즈 역으로 출연했다.','Karl-Heinz Urban','Wellington, New Zealand','1972-06-07',NULL,NULL,'KarlUrban.jpg'),(2549,'John Noble','존 노블','존 노블은 호주 출신의 배우로, 피터 잭슨의 반지의 제왕 3부작에서 데네소르 역을 연기한 것으로 유명하다.','','Port Pirie, South Australia, Australia','1948-08-20',NULL,NULL,'JohnNoble.jpg'),(2550,'Ian Holm','이안 홀름','Sir Ian Holm is an Academy Award-nominated British film and stage actor who was a star of the Royal Shakespeare Company, and played more than 100 roles in films and on television.\r\n\r\nHe was born Ian Holm Cuthbert on September 12, 1931, in Goodmayes, Essex, UK, to Scottish parents who worked at the Essex mental asylum. His mother, Jean Wilson (Holm), was as a nurse, and his father, Doctor James Harvey Cuthbert, was a psychiatrist. Young Holm was brought up in London. At the age of seven he was inspired by the seeing ‘Les Miserables‘ and became fond of acting. Holm studied at the Royal Academy of Dramatic Arts, graduating in 1950 to the Royal Shakespeare Company. There he emerged as an actor whose range and effortless style allowed him to play almost entire Shakespeare‘s repertoire. In 1959 his stage partner Laurence Olivier scored a hit on Ian Holm in a sword fight in a production of ‘Coriolanus‘. Holm still has a scar on his finger.\r\n\r\nIn 1965 Holm made his debut on television as Richard III on the BBC‘s The Wars of the Roses (1965), which was a filmed theatrical production of four of Shakespeare‘s plays condensed down into a trilogy. In 1969 Holm won his first BAFTA Film Award Best Supporting Actor for The Bofors Gun (1968), then followed a flow of awards and nominations for his numerous works in film and on television. In 1981 Holm shot to fame with one of his best known roles, as Sam Mussabini in Chariots of Fire (1981), for which he was nominated for Oscar for Best Actor in a Supporting Role. He is best known for his big action film roles, such as Father Vito Cornelius in The Fifth Element (1997), as Bilbo in The Lord of the Rings: The Return of the King (2003), and as Professor Fitz in The Aviator (2004).\r\n\r\nIan Holm has five children, three daughters and two sons from the first three of his five wives. In 1989 Holm was created a Commander of the British Empire (CBE), and in 1998 he was knighted for his services to drama.','Ian Holm Cuthbert','Goodmayes, Essex, England, UK','1931-09-12',NULL,NULL,'IanHolm.jpg'),(3534,'Bill Murray','빌 머레이','Bill, the fifth of nine children, was born in Wilmette, Illinois, to Lucille (Collins), a mailroom clerk, and Edward Joseph Murray II, who sold lumber. He is of Irish descent. Among his siblings are actors Brian Doyle-Murray, Joel Murray, and John Murray. He and most of his siblings worked as caddies, which paid his tuition to Loyola Academy, a Jesuit school. He played sports and did some acting while in that school, but in his words, mostly \"screwed off.\" He enrolled at Regis College in Denver to study pre-med but dropped out after being arrested for marijuana possession. He then joined the National Lampoon Radio Hour with fellow members Dan Aykroyd, Gilda Radner, and John Belushi. However, while those three became the original members of Saturday Night Live (1975), he joined Saturday Night Live with Howard Cosell (1975), which premiered that same year. After that show failed, he later got the opportunity to join Saturday Night Live (1975).','William James Murray','Wilmette, Illinois, USA','1950-09-21',NULL,NULL,'BillMurray.jpg'),(3535,'Keisha Castle-Hughes','케이샤 캐슬 휴즈','Keisha Castle-Hughes was born on March 24, 1990 in Donnybrook, Western Australia, Australia. She is an actress, known for Star Wars: Episode III - Revenge of the Sith (2005), Whale Rider (2002) and The Nativity Story (2006). She has been married to Jonathan Morrison since 2013.','','Donnybrook, Western Australia, Australia','1990-03-24',NULL,NULL,'KeishaCastle-Hughes.jpg'),(3536,'Diane Keaton','다이앤 키튼','Diane Keaton was born Diane Hall in Los Angeles, California, to Dorothy Deanne (Keaton), an amateur photographer, and John Newton Ignatius \"Jack\" Hall, a civil engineer and real estate broker. Her ancestry includes Irish, English, German, and Scottish.\r\n\r\nKeaton studied Drama at Santa Ana College before dropping out to study at the Neighborhood Playhouse in New York. After appearing in summer stock for several months, she got her first major stage role in the Broadway rock musical \"Hair.\" As understudy to the lead, she gained attention by not removing any of her clothing. In 1970, Woody Allen cast her in his Broadway play \"Play It Again, Sam,\" which had a successful run. It was during this time that she became involved with Allen and appeared in a number of his films. The first one was Play It Again, Sam (1972), the screen adaptation of the stage play. That same year Francis Ford Coppola cast her as Kay in the Oscar-winning The Godfather (1972), and she was on her way to stardom. She reprized that role in the film‘s first sequel, The Godfather: Part II (1974). She then appeared with Allen again in Sleeper (1973) and Love and Death (1975).\r\n\r\nIn 1977 she broke away from her comedy image to appear in the chilling Looking for Mr. Goodbar (1977), which won her a Golden Globe nomination. It was the same year that she appeared in what many regard as her best performance, in the title role of Annie Hall (1977), which Allen wrote specifically for her (her real last name is Hall, and her nickname is Annie), and what an impact she made. She won the Oscar and the British Award for Best Actress, and Allen won the Directors Award from the DGA. She started a fashion trend with her unisex clothes and was the poster girl for a lot of young males. Her mannerisms and awkward speech became almost a national craze. The question being asked, though, was, \"Is she just a lightweight playing herself, or is there more depth to her personality?\" For whatever reason, she appeared in but one film a year for the next two years and those films were by Allen. When they broke up she was next involved with Warren Beatty and appeared in his film Reds (1981), as the bohemian female journalist Louise Bryant. For her performance she received nominations for the Academy Award and the Golden Globe. For the rest of the 1980s she appeared infrequently in films but won nominations in three of them. Attempting to break the typecasting she had fallen into, she took on the role of a confused, somewhat naive woman who becomes the tool of Middle Eastern terrorists in The Little Drummer Girl (1984). To offset her lack of movie work, Diane began directing. She directed the documentary Heaven (1987), as well as some music videos. For television she directed an episode of the popular, but strange, Twin Peaks (1990).\r\n\r\nIn the 1990s she began to get more mature roles, though she reprized the role of Kay Corleone in the third \"Godfather\" epic, The Godfather: Part III (1990). She appeared as the wife of Steve Martin in the hit Father of the Bride (1991) and again in Father of the Bride Part II (1995). In 1993 she once again teamed with Woody Allen in Manhattan Murder Mystery (1993), which was well received. In 1995 she received high marks for Unstrung Heroes (1995), her first major feature as a director.','Diane Hall','Los Angeles, California, USA','1946-01-05',NULL,NULL,'DianeKeaton.jpg'),(3537,'Michael Bay','마이클 베이','마이클베이는 20편이 넘는 광고와 뮤직비디오를 연출한 재능있는 감독이었다. 그는 티나 터너, 미트 로프, 라이오넬 리치, 윌슨 필립스의 뮤직 비디오를 연출했으며, 그가 연출한 많은 뮤직비지오는 MTV Award에서 인정받았다. 그는 나이키, 리복, 코카몰라, 버드와이저, 밀러 맥주 광고를 연출했으며, 여러 광고상을 휩쓸었다. 여기서 연출력을 인정받은 그는 윌 스미스와 마틴 로렌스가 출연한 \"나쁜 녀석들(1995년)\"을 연출했으며, 숀 코넬리, 니콜라스 케이지와 \"더 록(1996년)\"을 연출해 스타 감독이 되었다. 그후 \"아마겟돈(1998년)\", \"진주만(2001년)\"을 연출했으며, 게리 브룩하이머와 결별한 후 \"아일랜드(2005년)\"를 감독했고, 후에트랜스포머 1, 2, 3를 감독했다.','Michael Benjamin Bay','Los Angeles, California, USA','1965-02-17',NULL,NULL,'MichaelBay.jpg'),(3538,'Patty Jenkins','패티 젠킨스','Patty Jenkins was born on July 24, 1971 in George Air Force Base, Victorville, California, USA as Patricia Lea Jenkins. She is a director and writer, known for Monster (2003), Five (2011) and Velocity Rules (2001). She has been married to Sam Sheridan since September 1, 2007.','Patricia Lea Jenkins','George Air Force Base, Victorville, California, USA','1971-07-24',NULL,NULL,'PattyJenkins.jpg'),(3539,'Gore Verbinski','고어 버빈스키','Gore Verbinski, one of American cinema‘s most inventive directors who was a punk-rock guitarist as a teenager and had to sell his guitar to buy his first camera, is now the director of Pirates of the Caribbean: Dead Man‘s Chest (2006) which made the industry record for highest opening weekend of all time ($135,600,000) and grossed over $1 billion','Gregor Verbinski','Oak Ridge, Tennessee, USA','1964-03-16',NULL,NULL,'GoreVerbinski.jpg'),(3540,'Nancy Meyers','낸시 마이어스','Nancy Meyers was born on December 8, 1949 in Pennsylvania, USA as Nancy Jane Meyers. She is a writer and producer, known for The Holiday (2006), Something‘s Gotta Give (2003) and The Parent Trap (1998). She was previously married to Charles Shyer.','Nancy Jane Meyers','Pennsylvania, USA','1949-11-08',NULL,NULL,'NancyMeyers.jpg'),(3541,'Wolfgang Petersen','볼프강 피터슨','Wolfgang Petersen was born on March 14, 1941 in Emden, Germany. He is a director and writer, known for Troy (2004), Das Boot (1981) and The NeverEnding Story (1984). He has been married to Maria-Antoinette Borgel since 1978. He was previously married to Ursula Sieg.','','Emden, Germany','1941-03-14',NULL,NULL,'Wolfgan